  "body": "- [X] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nI ran truffle debug and it halts with the output \"stepping\".\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nI have a contract with this piece of code: \r\n```(bool success,) = msg.sender.call(\r\n            abi.encodeWithSignature(\r\n                \"receiveFlashLoan(uint256)\",\r\n                amount\r\n            )\r\n        );\r\n```\r\nThe tx failed near here. When I run truffle debug, it halts until this line. It works fine when debugging other txid. Only this specific txid has issues.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nIt should let me continue entering `n` to keep inspecting.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n<img width=\"668\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-09-03 at 1 56 30 AM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19768276/131893468-2d9b78b4-8e63-47a4-b4bd-9157734bd317.png\">\r\n\r\n<img width=\"248\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-09-03 at 1 56 06 AM\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19768276/131893420-c13f7417-9eb5-4b01-818d-11047caf5c94.png\">\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Mac OS\r\n* Ethereum client: Infura\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.4.8\r\n* node version (`node --version`): 16.7.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 7.20.3\r\n",
